FBIS3-33237 "drlat035_o_94002" FBIS-LAT-94-035 Document Type:Daily Report 22 Feb 1994 Colombia Anti-U.S. Groups Attack Baptist, Mormon Churches PA1902042994 Santa Fe de Bogota Emisoras Caracol Network in Spanish 1200 GMT 18 Feb 94 PA1902042994 Santa Fe de Bogota Emisoras Caracol Network Language: Spanish Article Type:BFN [From the "Caracol's 0600-0900" newscast] [Text] Cali -- Two churches, one Baptist and one Mormon, were the targets of terrorist attacks this week in southern Cali. Responsibility for the attacks has been claimed by groups opposed to the presence of U.S. troops in Juanchaco.
